%N A014908 Inverse of 899th cyclotomic polynomial.
%C A014908 Periodic with period length 899. - _Ray Chandler_, Apr 06 2017
%H A014908 Ray Chandler, <a href="/A014908/b014908.txt">Table of n, a(n) for n = 0..1000</a>
%H A014908 <a href="/index/Per#periodic">Index entries for periodic sequences</a>, period 899.
%H A014908 <a href="/index/Rec#order_840">Index entries for linear recurrences with constant coefficients</a>, order 840.
%H A014908 <a href="/index/Pol#poly_cyclo_inv">Index to sequences related to inverse of cyclotomic polynomials</a>
%p A014908 with(numtheory,cyclotomic); c := n->series(1/cyclotomic(n,x),x,80);
%o A014908 (PARI) first(n)=Vec(1/polcyclo(899)+O(x^(n+1))) \\ _Charles R Greathouse IV_, Jun 01 2026
